%BA%AFc-c%E1%BB%95-nguy%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%A3o-t%E1%BB%91ng-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-QwBhKgfBbSwRdGonGQ2iuw">Phú đắc cổ nguyên thảo tống biệt - 賦得古原草送別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%C3%ADch-hoa-t%E1%BB%A9-lu%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BB%99-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-T%C3%A0ng-Xu%C3%A2n-vi%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n-v%E1%BA%ADn-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-SsDEmZAqZiCiqdxXljqc0g">Tích hoa tứ luật bộ Tương Châu Tàng Xuân viên chủ nhân vận kỳ 1 - 惜花四律步湘州藏春園主人韻其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/Truy-t%C3%A1n-S%C3%B9ng-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/poem-nf_aweAmpODs7WkEPUpBpw">Truy tán Sùng Phạm thiền sư - 追贊崇范禪師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Lý Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A4u-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Ch%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%83-v%C3%B4-t%C6%B0-t%C3%A2m/poem-Sy8qPB5BelxLEt38l-xeew">Vô đề (Chân tể vô tư tâm) - 無題（真宰無私心）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A4u-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/author-ersmrUf9dYOiBelsjNNnnw">Vương Ấu Ngọc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
